description: If you’re looking for the best caffeinated beverages for your next event, you better believe that Brew Coffee Company has exactly what you need.This big bold trailer is brought to you by 3 passionate brothers who share a dream to be Atlanta’s number one mobile provider of 100% organic freshly-roasted handcrafted coffee. Taking Counter Culture’s high-quality beans and brewing them through their state-of-the-art equipment, they proudly serve delicious lattes, cappuccinos, iced coffees, teas, and more. Be sure to call on Brew if you wish for a coffee shop experience (complete with quality and care) right at your door!
name: Brew Coffee Company
